HEADWORD: Supraprotest
<hw>Su`pra*pro"test</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mercantile
Law)</fld> <def>An acceptance of a bill by a third person after protest
for nonacceptance by the drawee.</def> <rj><au>Burrill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
